Package: checkpoint
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Maximilian Dorninger <maximilian.dorninger@sz-ybbs.ac.at>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, python3-pip
Recommends: nodejs (>= 20)
Description: RFID checkpoint FastAPI service with Svelte frontend
 NFC reader checkpoint system with real-time WebSocket updates.
 Includes FastAPI backend and Svelte-based web UI.
 Starts automatically as a systemd service.
